Dedrone: Automatic Anti-Drone Security (URL: https://www.dedrone.com/en/)Dedrone is an airspace security plat- form that detects, classiﬁes, and miti- gates all drone threats.1) It enables airspace surveillance 24/7; 2) automated alarm &notiﬁ- cation; 3) multi-sensor analysis: RF sensor and vedio sensor; 4) DroneDNA analysis and pattern recognition capa- bilities for drone classiﬁcation.
